author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Man/Woman/Chainsaw performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded March 17, 2025.

Songs:
The Boss 00:41
Adam & Steve 03:46
What Lucy Found There 06:33
Ode To Clio 09:54
 
Billy Ward - Guitar, vocals
Vera Leppänen - Bass, Vocals

Lola Cherry - Drums
